ving, and fading at a rate of almost 1 %\nper year. Future observations could test this prediction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Sep 2009 17:20:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2009 15:14:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
