rror values, so that detections of lithium-6 can not safely\nbe claimed despite of the high resolving power (R ~ 95 000) and S/N (400-600).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Sep 2009 18:18:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-29"}
